Sum=0
  While True
     a=i
      if a==-1
        break
        sum=sum+a
        avg=sum/2
    print(sum)
    print(avg) 
INPUT:56,78,-98,-4,8,-1
OUTPUT:
Sum of positive numbers: 142.0
Average of positive numbers: 47.333333333333336
Sum of negative numbers: -102.0
Average of negative numbers: -51.0
